So I was thinking, you know, this station that's hated by so many people has to be doing something right.
I've got to go see what this is all about.
And I also wanted to go see Central Command, which was 10 minutes away, and that way I could get access to how this news was being created on the Arab side reaching the Arab world, and on the U.S. and Western side reaching the U.S.
And when I went there and sat there, and met these people that were in the center of it and sat with these characters, I met some surprising, very complex people.
