<title>Emily Levine: A theory of everything</title>
<description>Philosopher-comedian Emily Levine talks about science, math, society and the way everything connects. She's a brilliant trickster, poking holes in our fixed ideas and bringing hidden truths to light. Settle in and let her ping your brain.</description>
